name: abbeytouchette
review: Pastor Carl is a wonderful, God fearing man, who preaches the Bible. His knowledge, passion and love of Jesus will help you in your understandings of God and His plans for all of us.

name: Caleb Maltby (Themeridian)
review: A great little church that desires nothing less than the proclamation of the Whole Council of God. Wonderful, heart-warming fellowship to be found here!
